&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Certified Veterinary Technician&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salary: &lt;/strong&gt;$23.00 - $29.00 per hour, &amp;nbsp;determined by the candidate&#39;s skills, experience, and qualifications.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Schedule:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Four 10-hour shifts (7:45am-6pm) with a designated day off. 36-40 hours per week. No weekend hours!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Park Grove Pet Hospital i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;s hiring a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;full-time &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Certified Veterinary Technician to provide skilled care to our patients and exceptional service to our clients. Our ideal candidate has experience in animal care, client communication, and veterinary procedures, with a passion for improving the lives of pets and their owners.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
